<note n="0386001" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0386001">言＝說【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0386002" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0386002">已＝以【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note>
